Core Features
- Administration & Configuration
- Sharing Settings
- Fullscreen Mode (on all Smart TVs)
- Print Dashboards
- Export Dashboard and send to email
- Presentation Mode (Per Dashboard, All Dashboards, Visualisations Selected)
- Multiple and configurable Layouts for Dashboards (ODK, Excel, SQL, API, Elastic Search, etc.)
- External Data Sources beyond DHIS2 ********************************
- Flexible Color Themes for dashboards.
- Public (DHIS2 and Portal Approach) and Secure Access


